---
import { Star } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<section id="testimonials" class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          What Our Customers Say
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          Real reviews from real Toronto homeowners
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Reviews Grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
              <Star class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500" />
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            "Joe and his crew replaced our 30-year-old driveway. They showed up when they said they would, 
            finished on time, and the price was exactly what they quoted. No BS, just good honest work."
          </p>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Frank M.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Etobicoke - Driveway Replacement</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
              <Star class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500" />
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            "Had water coming into the basement for years. ImperialForm fixed it properly - 
            haven't had a drop of water in 3 years now. Worth every penny."
          </p>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Susan Chen</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">North York - Foundation Waterproofing</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
              <Star class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500" />
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            "Got quotes from 5 companies. Joe wasn't the cheapest but he was the only one who 
            explained everything properly. Glad we chose them - beautiful stamped patio!"
          </p>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">The Johnstons</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Scarborough - Patio Installation</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
              <Star class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500" />
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            "My parents used ImperialForm 20 years ago. When I needed my driveway done, 
            I didn't even get other quotes. Same great service, same fair pricing."
          </p>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Tony R.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Mississauga - Driveway & Walkway</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
              <Star class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500" />
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            "City said our sidewalk was a trip hazard and had to be fixed. Joe handled everything 
            including the permits. Fixed in 2 days, city inspector happy, we're happy."
          </p>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Margaret D.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Toronto - Sidewalk Repair</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
              <Star class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500" />
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            "Garage floor was cracking and pitting. They ground it down and applied epoxy coating. 
            Looks like a showroom now. Clean, professional crew. Highly recommend."
          </p>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Mike & Lisa K.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Vaughan - Garage Floor Coating</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust badges -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-1">500+</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">5-Star Reviews</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-1">A+</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">BBB Rating</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-1">39</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Years in Business</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-1">100%</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Licensed & Insured</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>